* Table Format\nDecision Criteria
** Start with Delta Lake
***_ Default choice
***_ Best Databricks integration
** Consider Iceberg When
***_ Multi-engine access needed
***_ Org standardized on Iceberg
***_ Interop with Snowflake / Athena
** Use CSV/JSON Only
***_ Landing zone
***_ Small non-analytics data
** Key Dimensions
***_ Analytics performance
***_ ACID transactions
***_ Cross-platform compatibility
***_ Production readiness
